text: Wojciech Mickunas (born 16 March 1947) is a Polish equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Poland Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:People from Konin County Category:Sportspeople from Greater Poland Voivodeship
